{"tid":1346242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 唔好再叫人淨係放焦點係上環 黑社會之後先清算","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:09:22.000Z","uid":282889,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"898c8806c2fd785e69afee5761dd178382b91059","tid":1346242,"uid":282889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:47:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喺要2樣一齊講！</span><br />\n<br />\n根本成件事好大可能係克警嘅策略嚟嘅<br />\n<br />\n黑社會點打人 文宣可以細力啲<br />\n但警方故意放人、999無人聽、999叫人驚就唔好出街、報案室落閘、成晚拉1個人、警黑合作<br />\n呢啲位一定要大大力咁文宣<br />\n拆對家個台 比壓力警察 實施圍魏救趙之計<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">而家仲有好多元朗人被困啊！黑社會仲橫行無忌啊！喺咪唔救佢地啊！</span><br />\n<br />\n同一時間都要大力文宣警方唔聲唔聲係上環無預警下開咗30槍  過分武力<br />\n<br />\n正如開頭所講 成件事好大可能係克警策略嚟嘅 <br />\n而家警方就喺試圖利用元朗事件減輕開槍嘅輿論壓力<br />\n或者利用開槍嘅事掩蓋警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果我地淨喺講一樣唔講一樣 就係中曬佢地計 所以一定要2樣一齊講！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"fd36ee96e689d8076a8ebb674a068da32e2f9018","tid":1346242,"uid":282889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ebbbfd552db9c19b47303d5a0d63d897f7f979","tid":1346242,"uid":282889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"唔好中計啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0635cf8cbeabe928b793097703c5f22460d7ccce","tid":1346242,"uid":282197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:50:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90d2ce1ff498337dd3390d015aad4ec4c5fe636e","tid":1346242,"uid":282889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:52:00.000Z","msg":"幫手推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343f4e8f491d5042698822cb383010d28ddba431","tid":1346242,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci